## Registration Summary

| Metric              | Count |
|---------------------|------:|
| Capacity            | {{ event.capacity }} |
| Confirmed           | {{ stats.confirmed_count }} |
| Waitlisted          | {{ stats.waitlisted_count }} |
| VIP                 | {{ stats.vip_count }} |
| High no-show risk   | {{ stats.high_risk_count }} |
| Fill rate           | {{ (stats.fill_ratio * 100) | round(1) }}% |

{% if stats.waitlisted_count > 0 %}
> ℹ️ **Waitlist active.** If registrants do not check in by
> {{ event.starts_at | timedelta(minutes=15) | time_format('%H:%M') }},
> consider offering waitlisted spots.
{% endif %}

