## High No-Show Risk Registrants ({{ stats.high_risk_count }})

{% if flagged_registrants %}
Consider sending a same-day reminder to the following registrants before
{{ event.starts_at | timedelta(hours=-2) | time_format('%H:%M') }}:

| Name | Email | Predicted no-show % |
|------|-------|--------------------:|
{% for r in flagged_registrants %}
| {{ r.name }} | {{ r.email }} | {{ (r.no_show_prob * 100) | round(0) | int }}% |
{% endfor %}
{% else %}
No high-risk no-show registrants detected.
{% endif %}

