## Contingency Checklist

- [ ] A/V backup plan confirmed
- [ ] Overflow room available if attendance exceeds capacity
- [ ] First aid contact briefed
- [ ] Dietary labels on all catering items
- [ ] Accessibility paths clear (ramps, hearing loops tested)
- [ ] Waitlist notification sent if no-shows materialise
- [ ] Post-event survey trigger scheduled (see outputs/post-event-survey-trigger)

